Class MeshLambertMaterial

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public final class MeshLambertMaterial
extends Material
implements HasMaterialMap, HasWrap, HasWireframe, HasFog, HasVertexColors, HasSkinning, HasAmbientEmissiveColor, HasShading
    A material for non-shiny (Lambertian) surfaces, evaluated per vertex.
